            <img src="/images/comingsoon.webp">
            <p>Gyu-Kaku, meaning "Horn of the Bull" in Japanese, provides authentic grilled barbecue dining experience where customers share premium cooked meats over a flaming smokeless grill, while sipping on Japanese sake and cold beers.</p>
            <a href="">Menu</a>
